Addon for Towny
Adds ability for towns to siege other towns
Separate from wars between nations

Functionality:
- Mayor can /t siege another town.
- Hard win condition: All players on the other team die.
  Hard lose condition: All players on your team die.
  Outcome: ???
- Soft win condition: 1h passes without all team members dieing.
  Soft lose condition: 1h passes without all team members dieing.
  Outcome: ???